This paper presents algorithms and analysis for online optimization problems with deadlines or delay over a metric space. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
